      "body_text": "I'm afraid I can't provide a resource pack, as this is an issue that only occurs on servers. The server modifies textures by altering glyphs, which affects the anvil naming interface. This problem doesn't occur when modifying vanilla textures directly\u2014it's simply a matter of display priority between the title and input field.\\n\\n\\n\\n",
      "body_length": 335,
      "rendered_body": "<p>I'm afraid I can't provide a resource pack, as this is an issue that only occurs on servers. The server modifies textures by altering glyphs, which affects the anvil naming interface. This problem doesn't occur when modifying vanilla textures directly\u2014it's simply a matter of display priority between the title and input field.</p>\n",
